titles.title: I enter the holy of holies

verse.name: v1a
verse.lines:
I enter the holy of holies
I enter through the blood of the Lamb
I enter to worship You only
I enter to honor I Am

verse.lines:
Lord I worship You
I worship You
Lord I worship You
I worship You

verse.name: v1c
verse.lines:

For Your name is Holy, Holy Lord

We enter to honor I Am

verse.lines:
Lord we worship You
